<item>
            <title>[LU-19079] gss for nodemap identification</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-19079</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;If we want to be able to use GSS as a way to distinguish clients in nodemaps, we would need a new &lt;tt&gt;gss_identification&lt;/tt&gt; property. So let&apos;s reserve an LCFG_NODEMAP_ for it.&lt;br/&gt;
We would also potentially need another one to be able to lookup a nodemap based on the sha256 of its name, as sent from client to server as part of the gss context negotiation process.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
